wminc-desc: Sɔ wiki system hwɛ na gye Wiki Incubator
wminc-prefinfo-code: Kasa a iridzi ho dwuma wɔ ha no ho ISO 639 koodu
wminc-prefinfo-project: Yi wikimedia dwumadzi a iridzi ho dwuma no wɔ ha
wminc-prefinfo-error: Iyii dwumadzi a ohia kasa koodu
wminc-error-wronglangcode: Error: Dɛm kratafa yi wɔ [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|kasa koodu a ɔnnyɛ papa]] "$1".
wminc-error-unprefixed-suggest: Error: Dɛm kratafa yi yɛ: [[{{MediaWiki:Wminc-error-help}}|unprefixed]]! Ibotum ayɛ kratafa fofor wɔ [[:$1]].
wminc-error-wiki-exists: Dɛm wiki yi wɔ hɔ dada. Ibohu dɛm kratafa yi wɔ $1. Sɛ wɔyɛɛ wiki no nnkyɛree a, tweɔn dɔnhwer bi anaa nda kakra kɛpem dɛ nsɛm no bɛba.
wminc-error-wiki-sister: Dɛm kratafa yi yɛ dwumadzi a ɔnnkɔ do wɔ ha. Kɔ $1  na hwehwɛ wiki no.
wminc-viewuserlang: Hwehwɛ dwumadzinyi ne kasa na sɔ wiki hwɛ
wminc-ip: "$1" yɛ IP adrɛɛse anaa ber tsiaba mu dwumadzinyi.
action-viewuserlang: Hwɛ dwumadzinyi kasa na test wiki
right-viewuserlang: Hwɛ dwumadzinyi kasa na test wiki
wminc-search-nocreate-suggest: Ehwehwɛɛ "$1". Ibotum ayɛ krtafa wɔ wo wiki no mu wɔ [[$3]]!
wminc-searchwiki-match-englishname: "$1" yɛ dzin a wɔdze ma $2 wo Brɔfo mu.
wminc-infopage-contribute: Sɛ enyim dɛm kasa yi aa, yɛ hyɛ wo dzen dɛ kyerɛ w'adwen!
